{"kanda":6,"sarga":56,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"तद्दृष्टवासुमहत्कर्मकृतंवानरतस्तमैः ।क्रोधमाहारयामासयुधितीव्रमकम्पनः","trans":"Observing the great action and accomplishment of the foremost Vanaras in the battle, Akampana exhibited violent anger.","words":[{"d":"अकम्पनः","m":"Akampana"},{"d":"युधि","m":"in battle"},{"d":"वानरसत्तमैः","m":"foremost of Vanaras"},{"d":"कृतम्","m":"accomplishment"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"सुमहत्","m":"great"},{"d":"कर्म","m":"action"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"observing"},{"d":"तीव्रम्","m":"violent"},{"d":"क्रोधम्","m":"angry"},{"d":"आहारयामास","m":"exhibiting."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"क्रोधमूर्चितरूपस्तुधून्वन्परमकार्मुकम् ।दृष्टवातुकर्मशत्रूणांसारथिंवाक्यमब्रवीत्","trans":"Looking at the deeds of enemies, deluded with violent anger, Akampana spoke these words holding the bow and looking at the charioteer.","words":[{"d":"शत्रूणाम्","m":"by enemies"},{"d":"कर्म","m":"deeds"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"looking"},{"d":"क्रोधमूर्चितरूपः","m":"exhibited violent anger"},{"d":"परमकार्मुकम्","m":"highly furious"},{"d":"धून्वन्","m":"bow"},{"d":"सारथिम्","m":"charioteer"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"तत्त्त्वैतावत्त्वरितंरथंप्रापयसारथे ।यत्रैतेबहवोघ्नन्तिसुबहून्राक्षसान्रणे","trans":"\"O Charioteer, quickly drive the chariot to that place where many Rakshasas are destroyed in the battle.\"","words":[{"d":"सारथे","m":"O Charioteer"},{"d":"यत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"बहव:","m":"many"},{"d":"एते","m":"those"},{"d":"रणे","m":"in battle"},{"d":"सुबहून्","m":"many"},{"d":"राक्षसान्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"घ्नन्ति","m":"destroyed"},{"d":"त्वरितः","m":"quickly"},{"d":"तत्त्रैव","m":"to that place"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"प्रापय","m":"drive."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"एतेऽत्रबलवन्तोहिभीमकोपाश्चवानराः ।द्रुमशैलप्रहरणास्तिष्ठन्तिप्रमुखेमम","trans":"\"Those Vanaras are mighty and terribly angry. They are using trees and hillocks as weapons. Take me where chiefs are standing.\"","words":[{"d":"बलवन्तः","m":"mighty"},{"d":"भीमकोपाश्च","m":"terribly angry"},{"d":"एते","m":"those"},{"d":"वानराः","m":"Vanara"},{"d":"द्रुमशैलप्रहरणाः","m":"using trees and hillocks as weapons"},{"d":"अत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"प्रमुखे","m":"chiefs"},{"d":"तिष्ठन्तिहि","m":"stand."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"एतान्निहन्तुमिच्छामिसमरश्लाघिनोह्यहम् ।एतैःप्रमथितंसर्वंदृश्यतेराक्षसांबलम्","trans":"\"I wish to see the end of Vanaras who boast of their warfare. The entire Rakshasa army is destroyed by them.\"","words":[{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"समरश्लाघिनः","m":"boast of their warfare"},{"d":"एतान्","m":"them"},{"d":"निहन्तुम्","m":"will finish"},{"d":"इच्छामि","m":"desire to"},{"d":"रक्षसाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"all"},{"d":"बलम्","m":"army"},{"d":"एतैः","m":"in the same way"},{"d":"प्रमथिम्","m":"end"},{"d":"दृश्यते","m":"wish to see."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"ततःप्रजवनाश्वेनरथेनरथिनांवरः ।हरीनभ्यहनत्क्रोधाच्छरजालैकम्पनः","trans":"Then Akampana seated in the chariot drawn by fast moving horses, assailed the Vanaras with a network of arrows.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"रथिनाम्","m":"on the chariot"},{"d":"वरः","m":"foremost"},{"d":"अकम्पनः","m":"Akampana"},{"d":"प्रचलिताश्वेन","m":"by fast moving horses"},{"d":"रथेन","m":"from chariot"},{"d":"शरजालैः","m":"network of arrows"},{"d":"त्क्रोधात्","m":"enraged"},{"d":"हरीन्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"अभ्यहनत्","m":"assailed."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"नस्थातुंवानराश्शेकुःकिंपुनर्योद्धुमाहवे ।अकम्पनशरैर्भग्नास्सर्वएवविदुद्रुवुः","trans":"The Vanaras could not counter or stand nor fight in battle. What to say more? Shattered by Akampana's arrows, they all took to their heels.","words":[{"d":"वानराः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"आहवे","m":"counter"},{"d":"स्थातुम्","m":"to stand"},{"d":"नशेकुः","m":"not fight"},{"d":"योद्धुम्","m":"in battle"},{"d":"किंपुनः","m":"What to say again"},{"d":"सर्वेएव","m":"all"},{"d":"अकम्पनशरैः","m":"by Akampana's arrows"},{"d":"भग्नाः","m":"shattered"},{"d":"विदुद्रुवुः","m":"took to their heels."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"तान्मृत्यु