ुः","trans":"Again, and again looking back in fear, covertly, bewildered, crushing one another, they went into the Lanka city.","words":[{"d":"ते","m":"they"},{"d":"भयात्","m":"in fear"},{"d":"पृष्ठतः","m":"covertly"},{"d":"मुहुर्मुहुः","m":"again and again"},{"d":"प्रेक्षमाणाः","m":"looking back"},{"d":"सम्मूढाः","m":"bewildered"},{"d":"अन्योन्यम्","m":"one another"},{"d":"प्रममन्थु:","m":"crushing"},{"d":"नगरम्","m":"city"},{"d":"विविशुः","m":"went."}]},{"v":35,"dev":"तेषुलङ्कांप्रविष्टेषुराक्षसेषुमहाबलाः ।समेत्यहरयस्सर्वेहनूमन्तमपूजयन्","trans":"Those Rakshasas, endowed with prowess, on entering Lanka got together and paid respects to Hanuman.","words":[{"d":"तेषुराक्षसेषु","m":"those Rakshasas"},{"d":"लङ्काम्","m":"into Lanka"},{"d":"प्रविष्टेषु","m":"on entering"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"महाबलाः","m":"endowed with prowess"},{"d":"हरयः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"समेत्य","m":"getting together"},{"d":"हनूमन्तम्","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"अपूजयन्","m":"paid respects."}]},{"v":36,"dev":"सोऽपिप्रहृष्टस्तान् सर्वान् हरीन् सम्प्रत्यपूजयत् ।हनुमान्सत्त्वसम्पन्नोयथार्हमनुकूलतः","trans":"Hanuman also who was richly endowed with goodness greatly honoured all the Vanaras accordingly.","words":[{"d":"सत्त्वसम्पन्नः","m":"richly endowed with goodness"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"हनुमानपि","m":"Hanuman also"},{"d":"अनुकूलतः","m":"others for their part"},{"d":"यथार्हम्","m":"accordingly"},{"d":"तान्","m":"them"},{"d":"सर्वान्","m":"all"},{"d":"हरीन्","m":"monkeys"},{"d":"सम्प्रत्यपूजयत्","m":"greatly honoured."}]},{"v":37,"dev":"विनेदुश्चयथाप्राणंहरयोजितकाशिनः ।चकर्षुश्चपुनस्तत्रसप्राणानपिराक्षसान्","trans":"In an atmosphere of triumph, the monkeys sportively shouted again saying that they are willing to give up their life also.","words":[{"d":"जितकाशिनः","m":"atmosphere of triumph"},{"d":"हरयः","m":"monkeys"},{"d":"यथाप्राणम्","m":"their life"},{"d":"विनेदुः","m":"sportively"},{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"सप्राणानपि","m":"willing to give up their life"},{"d":"राक्षसान्","m":"Raks